headline: Tyler Technologies Schedules Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call and Webcast
summary: PLANO, Texas, January 27, 2026--Tyler Technologies will discuss its fourth quarter 2025 results during a conference call and webcast on Thursday, February 12, 2026.
